        <methods>
            <methodStep>
                <description>
                    <section>
                        <title>Fire Mapping</title>
                        <para>Imagery from NASA (MODIS) and NOAA (AVHRR) satellites is downloaded and processed using GIS software to identify and map fire scars for each month of the year. The processing includes detecting hot spots from current fires and using difference images to highlight previous fire scars.</para>
                    </section>
                </description>
                <instrumentation>ArcGIS 10.1, eCognition Developer8.6</instrumentation>
            </methodStep>
        </methods>
